== Overview ==
Run various linux commands on nodes

== Usage == 
Supported commands:
	reboot (protected) : reboots a node
	uptime : returnis the output of the uptime command
	postqueue : count or empty postfix mail queue
	tcpdump : start/stop tcp dump on node

Protected commands will ask for verification if asked without any filters.

== Installation ==
	Copy the agent, application and util directories into mcollective plugins dir (/usr/share/mcollective/plugins/mcollective/ on debian)
